               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined.</hi> There was a Mr. Mercer, a barrister, connected with the Inner Temple, but he had a certificate on the 1st May, 1874, and went to India, I believe within a week of that date—there has not been a Mr. John Pollard, for the last fifty-six years.</p>
