                  </hi>. I live at 53, Paradise Strect, Lambeth—I once lived at 89, Regent Street, Lambeth, eight or nine years since—I am a coroner's officer—I do not know the prisoner—I was never employed by him to trace out a draft or something in connection with a robbery—I never saw him until in custody at the Lambeth police-court, to my knowledge—I know nothing of a letter signed "I Shepherd," of Deptford, it is not ray writing—the receipt for two guineas I know nothing of—it does not bear my signature.</p>
