                        <interp inst="t18760131-191-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>—<hi rend="italic">Several previous convictions were proved against the prisoner.—<rs id="t18760131-191-punishment-39" type="punishmentDescription">
